  </div>
</div>

<div class="accessory carry-bag">
  <h3>Carry Bag</h3>

  <h4>Description</h4>
  <p>Soft sided, zippered bag for convenient organization
transportation. Bag is designed to accommodate
tool &amp; handle assembly.</p>
  <div class="display group">
    <img  src="/products/accessories/carry-bag.png" alt="Screw Pouch">

    <h5>VISCB701</h5>
    <p>For the CH7390, CH7241, &amp; CH7260
series of tools.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="accessory extension">
  <h3>Extension Handles</h3>

  <h4>Description</h4>
  <p>Telescopic T-handle provides the best fit, balance and height adjustment for the user.</p>

  <div class="display group">
    <img  src="/products/accessories/visrh909-handle.png" alt="VISRH909 Extension Handle">
    <h5>VISRH909</h5>
    <p>For the CH7241 &amp; CH7390</p>
    <h5>VISRH912</h5>
    <p>For the CH7260 series</p>
  </div>

  <div class="display group">
    <img  src="/products/accessories/visrh910-handle.png" alt="VISRH910 Extension Handle">
    <h5>VISRH910</h5>
    <p>For the HDVL71 tool.</p>
    <h5>VISRH902</h5>
    <p>For the FDVL41, FLVL41 coil tools.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="display group">
    <img  src="/products/accessories/visrh905-handle.png" alt="VISRH905 Extension Handle">
    <h5>VISRH905</h5>
    <p>Serves the VL62 family of coil tools.</p>
  </div>
</div>

